Using these models we’ll compare each of their performance

comp <- compare_performance(mod1,mod2,mod3,mod4,mod5, rank = TRUE)
## When comparing models, please note that probably not all models were fit
##   from same data.
comp %>% plot()

according to this chart, it appears that mod5 outperforms the other tested modules but appears to be over-fitting, whereas mod4 may be a better option.
